flowchart TD
    Resume([Your resume]) --> Understand[Agent learns your skills,<br/>target roles, and location]

    Understand --> Search[Search live job listings]

    Search --> Match[Score each job<br/>against your background]

    Match --> Dashboard[Save the best matches<br/>to your dashboard]

    Dashboard --> Review([You review matches<br/>and choose what to apply to])

    Match --> Improve[Learn from jobs that fit well]

    Improve --> Smarter[Update search terms]

    Smarter --> Search

    Schedule[Runs once a day automatically<br/>or anytime you click Run cycle now] -.-> Search

    style Resume fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a5f
    style Review fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#2563eb,color:#1e3a5f
    style Dashboard fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d
    style Schedule fill:#fef9c3,stroke:#ca8a04,color:#713f12
